# Structure

This is an overview of the general format of the [Medicare Physician Fee Schedule (MPFS)](https://www.cms.gov/medicare/payment/fee-schedules/physician), specifically the [PFS Relative Value File](https://www.cms.gov/medicare/payment/fee-schedules/physician/pfs-relative-value-files). Updates are released on the first day of each quarter. If required, a correction notice may be issued. The file is a zip archive and typically contains six files:




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
dplyr::tibble(
  `Naming Convention` = c(
    p("<b>RVU[</b>",
      "<i><small>YY</small></i>",
      "<b>]A</b>",
      ".zip"
      ),
    p("RVU[YY]AR.zip"),
    p("RVU[YY]B.zip"),
    p("RVU[YY]C.zip"),
    p("RVU[YY]D.zip")
  ),
  `Release Schedule` = c(
    p("Q1: January 1<sup>st</sup>"),
    p("Q1: January ??",
      "<br><br>",
      "<small><b>Correction Notice</b><br>(If Required)</small>"
      ),
    p("Q2: April 1<sup>st</sup>"),
    p("Q3: July 1<sup>st</sup>"),
    p("Q4: October 1<sup>st</sup>")
  )
) |> 
  gt::gt(process_md = TRUE) |> 
  gt::fmt_markdown() |> 
  # gt::opt_table_font(font = gt::google_font(name = "Roboto Slab")) |> 
  gt::tab_header("PFS RVU File Release Schedule") |>
  gt::opt_all_caps() |>
  gt::tab_options(
    heading.align = "left",
    heading.border.bottom.color = "#555555", # "#4758AB",
    heading.title.font.weight = "bold",
    heading.background.color = "#555555", # "#f8f9fa",
    quarto.disable_processing = TRUE,
    data_row.padding.horizontal = gt::px(20),
    column_labels.padding.horizontal = gt::px(20),
    table.border.top.color = "#555555",
    table.width = gt::pct(100))
```

